Job:CiamShared230_Load_SixNode
Project : EDW CIAM
Developer:  Manikanteswara Gogula
Date : 16-Sep-2024

Description : This is a MLOAD job with Multi node configuration which will load data from Kafka Flat files and load to target staging tables using schema files and Runtime Column Propagation.
This job will be called dynamically during the runtime based on the volume of the data.                  

Before Routine: NA
After Routine: CiamShared080_FileArchive.ksh

Restart Procedure: Rerun the Job

